  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will investigate the effects of methylphenidate on sleep in adults with Attention
      Deficit/ Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD) using polysomnographic parameters.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Previous studies in children with Attention Deficit/ Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD) have
      described the effect of stimulants on sleep patterns. However the data on adults with ADHD is
      sparse.

      The aim of this study is to investigate the effects of methylphenidate on sleep in adults
      with ADHD using polysomnographic parameters.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
